---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="404 - Página no encontrada" 
  description="La página que buscas no existe. Regresa al inicio del portfolio de Deanny Bruces para explorar proyectos y contenido sobre desarrollo web."
  keywords="404, página no encontrada, error, Deanny Bruces"
>

<style>
  .not-found {
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100vw;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--bg-color, #f2e9f2);
    color: var(--h1-h2-color, #6e6b6b);
    border-radius: 0;
    box-shadow: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    animation: fadeInMove 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1) both;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .not-found-content {
    z-index: 1;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius, 20px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(80, 12, 75, 0.12);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    width: 90vw;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .not-found h1 {
    font-size: 6rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color, #c38cf6);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    animation: bounce404 1.5s infinite alternate;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 16px var(--secondary-color, #c38cf6);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .not-found h1:hover {
    transform: scale(1.15) rotate(-5deg);
    filter: brightness(1.2);
  }
  .not-found h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--primary-color, #2d0c4b);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: fadeInText 1.5s 0.5s both;
  }
  .not-found p {
    color: var(--text-color, #817d7d);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: fadeInText 1.5s 0.8s both;
  }
  .not-found a {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--acento-btn, #dda0dd);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition:
      background 0.3s,
      transform 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(195, 140, 246, 0.15);
    animation: fadeInText 1.5s 1.1s both;
  }
  .not-found a:hover {
    background: var(--acento-btn-hover, #c38cf6);
    transform: scale(1.08);
  }
  @keyframes fadeInMove {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px) scale(0.95);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
  }
  @keyframes bounce404 {
    0% {
      transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1.08) translateY(-10px);
    }
  }
  @keyframes fadeInText {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .not-found-content {
      padding: 2rem 0.5rem;
      max-width: 98vw;
    }
    .not-found h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
    .not-found h2 {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
  /* Decorative SVGs */
  .svg-deco {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.18;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: floatDeco 6s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .svg-deco.top {
    top: -40px;
    left: -40px;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    fill: var(--secondary-color, #c38cf6);
  }
  .svg-deco.bottom {
    bottom: -40px;
    right: -40px;
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    fill: var(--primary-color, #2d0c4b);
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }
  @keyframes floatDeco {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(20px) scale(1.08);
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="not-found">
  <svg class="svg-deco top" viewBox="0 0 100 100"
    ><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="50"></circle></svg
  >
  <svg class="svg-deco bottom" viewBox="0 0 100 100"
    ><rect x="10" y="10" width="80" height="80" rx="20"></rect></svg
  >
  <div class="not-found-content">
    <h1 tabindex="0">404</h1>
    <h2>Página no encontrada</h2>
    <p>Lo sentimos, la página que buscas no existe o fue movida.</p>
    <a href="/">Volver al inicio</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
